adqlParser.query.function
Class InFunction

java.lang.Object
  adqlParser.query.ADQLConstraint
      adqlParser.query.function.ADQLFunction
          adqlParser.query.function.InFunction
All Implemented Interfaces:
ADQLObject, ADQLOperand
public class InFunction
extends ADQLFunction

It represents the In function of SQL and ADQL.
This functions returns true if the value of the given operand is either in the given values list or in the results of the given sub-query, else it returns false.

Version:
06/2010
Author:
Grégory Mantelet (CDS)
